{"tid":201974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"土衞二含氫氣　能孕育微生物","createTime":"2017-04-15T07:03:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-15T20:10:05.000Z","uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8ce66213c944b94596641ad2293d2b1fd47e3732","tid":201974,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T07:03:18.000Z","msg":"適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170415/large/15we1p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170415%2Flarge%2F15we1p.jpg&h=670008d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■美國太空總署的示意圖，展示「卡西尼號」（箭嘴示）前年進入土衞二深海熱泉噴發的羽流。<br />\n科學界探索外星生命再有重大進展。美國太空總署（NASA）前日在《科學》期刊發表研究結果，指土星衞星土衞二（Enceladus）的地下海洋有氫氣湧出，可以提供維持生命所需的能量，或預示該處能夠孕育微生物。<br />\n<br />\nNASA根據環繞土星運行的探測船「卡西尼號」（Cassini）在2015年10月所拍得的影像，發現土衞二南極位置一處深海熱泉噴發出的羽流當中，含有98%的水和1%的氫氣，另外還有少量的氨、二氧化碳和甲烷等。<br />\n科學家解釋，氫氣之所以存在，是因為星球核心的熱岩石和海水之間產生了化學反應，因而生成。在這種成份的大氣環境下，氫和二氧化碳可以結合出甲烷，即所謂「甲烷生成」（Methanogenesis）過程，讓微生物獲得維持生命所需的能量。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170415/large/15we2p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170415%2Flarge%2F15we2p.jpg&h=5e8d3415&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■表層長年冰封的土衞二，是地球以外最有可能支持生命存在的太陽系星體之一。　<br />\n像「糖果店」提供食物<br />\n現時科學界一般相信，微生物之所以能夠在地球生成初期出現，也是因為類似的化學過程，因此NASA相信，土衞二擁有孕育生命的潛力。今次研究結果，是科學界至今在外星找到生命存在條件的最直接證據。<br />\n領導是次研究的韋特指出：「如今土衞二在太陽系最可能有生命的星體名單中，佔高排名。」他強調雖仍未在土衞二找到真正的生物，但該處就像一間「糖果店」，為生物提供必要的食物。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170415/large/a1101a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170415%2Flarge%2Fa1101a.gif&h=d58f2a83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n土衞二表層長年冰封，過去一般相信由於距離太陽過遠，難以孕育生命，不過科學家前年證實該星地底有液態海洋，找到生物的機會因而大增。要產生生命所需的能量，至少需要六項化學元素，包括碳、氫、氮、氧、磷和硫。目前在土衞二中仍未發現磷和硫，不過科學家傾向相信它們存在，因該星球核心的化學成份，與有這兩種物質的隕石類似。<br />\n科學家亦在另一研究中，利用「哈勃」太空望遠鏡發現木星衞星木衞二（Europa）上有羽流噴發，進一步證實該處也有地底海洋，同樣有孕育生命的潛力，需進一步研究其化學成份。<br />\n法新社/英國《每日郵報》  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170415/19990561\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170415%2F19990561&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2BQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=75c13c9b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170415%2F19990561&h=ebd97de9\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170415/19990561</a>"},{"pid":"ab19e28862d1e580a5820b7708137067e544ebeb","tid":201974,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T07:23:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cc29f8c35c83f1d54d78d28e8a2872bdf42c525","tid":201974,"uid":60129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T07:23:45.000Z","msg":"咁有冇可能第時搵到隻外星人，而佢又冇呢6種基本物質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23d1388b8326a379d19f603b0c931e77a2ec2a9e","tid":201974,"uid":34005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T07:26:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁有冇可能第時搵到隻外星人，而佢又冇呢6種基本物質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當然唔排除有咁既可能性<br />\n<br />\n科學家好多時都以地球生存條件出發<br />\n探索有冇類似地球既外星環境<br />\n因為目前科學理論可以解釋到既<br />\n係因為有地球呢d元素組合起黎 先結合到生命"},{"pid":"20078c16ec6e2c5b332b515d2d5ebe0e21810ef7","tid":201974,"uid":56954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:42:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁有冇可能第時搵到隻外星人，而佢又冇呢6種基本物質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當然唔排除有咁既可能性<br />\n<br />\n科學家好多時都以地球生存條件出發<br />\n探索有冇類似地球既外星環境<br />\n因為目前科學理論可以解釋到既<br />\n係因為有地球呢d元素組合起黎 先結合到生命</blockquote><br />\n係<br />\n但亦唔排除有唔駛水同oxygen都生存到既生物<br />\n只係現今科學未解釋到"},{"pid":"38795d506aa79b6f5be2ccc8018713372cdbd9eb","tid":201974,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T16:56:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5e2ada5a5cef127d4edba42023d95de08938ba8","tid":201974,"uid":43721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T18:21:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6837db1b03f8b22209373f734b9e133f11f34dce","tid":201974,"uid":26115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T19:29:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁有冇可能第時搵到隻外星人，而佢又冇呢6種基本物質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當然唔排除有咁既可能性<br />\n<br />\n科學家好多時都以地球生存條件出發<br />\n探索有冇類似地球既外星環境<br />\n因為目前科學理論可以解釋到既<br />\n係因為有地球呢d元素組合起黎 先結合到生命</blockquote><br />\n係<br />\n但亦唔排除有唔駛水同oxygen都生存到既生物<br />\n只係現今科學未解釋到</blockquote><br />\n地球上都有呢類微生物啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E7%BC%93%E6%AD%A5%E5%8A%A8%E7%89%A9%E9%97%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-tw%2F%25E7%25BC%2593%25E6%25AD%25A5%25E5%258A%25A8%25E7%2589%25A9%25E9%2597%25A8&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2BQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=67845833\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E7%BC%93%E6%AD%A5%E5%8A%A8%E7%89%A9%E9%97%A8</a><br />\n真空+ 強幅射環境下可以生存18個月"},{"pid":"9aa6e5ddb033592772761b5c1bf5f7dc77bd507c","tid":201974,"uid":26115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T19:35:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁有冇可能第時搵到隻外星人，而佢又冇呢6種基本物質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當然唔排除有咁既可能性<br />\n<br />\n科學家好多時都以地球生存條件出發<br />\n探索有冇類似地球既外星環境<br />\n因為目前科學理論可以解釋到既<br />\n係因為有地球呢d元素組合起黎 先結合到生命</blockquote><br />\n係<br />\n但亦唔排除有唔駛水同oxygen都生存到既生物<br />\n只係現今科學未解釋到</blockquote><br />\n地球上都有呢類微生物啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E7%BC%93%E6%AD%A5%E5%8A%A8%E7%89%A9%E9%97%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-tw%2F%25E7%25BC%2593%25E6%25AD%25A5%25E5%258A%25A8%25E7%2589%25A9%25E9%2597%25A8&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2BQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=67845833\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E7%BC%93%E6%AD%A5%E5%8A%A8%E7%89%A9%E9%97%A8</a><br />\n真空+ 強幅射環境下可以生存18個月</blockquote><br />\n糾正: 真空係幾分鐘，強幅射先係18個月"},{"pid":"074b4be8bd8bb7edbc583bccc09267a4f4e0b7b4","tid":201974,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T20:10:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁有冇可能第時搵到隻外星人，而佢又冇呢6種基本物質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當然唔排除有咁既可能性<br />\n<br />\n科學家好多時都以地球生存條件出發<br />\n探索有冇類似地球既外星環境<br />\n因為目前科學理論可以解釋到既<br />\n係因為有地球呢d元素組合起黎 先結合到生命</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 慕隊長博學多才"}]}